      <structureContents ID="3671">
        <structureContent lang="de">
          <structureText>Reglement<break type="line"/>&#xFC;ber die Revision der Besoldungskonzeption der Gerichtsschreiber</structureText>
        </structureContent>
        <structureContent lang="fr">
          <structureText>R&#xE8;glement<break type="line"/>concernant la r&#xE9;vision du concept salarial des greffiers</structureText>
        </structureContent>
      </structureContents>
      <normTexts>
        <article>
          <articleMetadata ID="Article:12492">
            <articleForm>Art.</articleForm>
            <articleNumber>
              <number>1</number>
            </articleNumber>
            <articleHeaders>
              <articleHeader>
                <mixedText lang="de">&#xDC;bergangsrecht</mixedText>
              </articleHeader>
              <articleHeader>
                <mixedText lang="fr">Droit transitoire</mixedText>
              </articleHeader>
            </articleHeaders>
          </articleMetadata>
          <articleBody>
            <articleText>
              <partMetadata ID="Paragraph:28763">
                <partNumber>1</partNumber>
                <typeOfPart>A</typeOfPart>
              </partMetadata>
              <partTexts>
                <partText>
                  <mixedText lang="de">Die bisherigen Erfahrungsanteile der Schreiber des Kantonsgerichts, der Bezirksgerichte und des Jugendgerichts werden mit Inkrafttreten des Gesetzes &#xFC;ber die Revision der Besoldungskonzeption vom 20. Juni 1995 gem&#xE4;ss der nachfolgenden Tabelle in neue Erfahrungsanteile umgewandelt:<table><tableContent><row rowType="header"><cell>Fr&#xFC;here Erfahrungsanteile</cell><cell>Prozent</cell><cell>Neue Erfahrungsanteile</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>1</cell><cell>3%</cell><cell>1.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>2</cell><cell>6%</cell><cell>3</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>3</cell><cell>9%</cell><cell>4.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>4</cell><cell>12%</cell><cell>6</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>5</cell><cell>15%</cell><cell>7.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>6</cell><cell>18%</cell><cell>9</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>7</cell><cell>21%</cell><cell>10.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>8</cell><cell>24%</cell><cell>12</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>9</cell><cell>27%</cell><cell>13.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>10</cell><cell>30%</cell><cell>15</cell></row></tableContent></table></mixedText>
                </partText>
                <partText>
                  <mixedText lang="fr">Lors de l'entr&#xE9;e en vigueur de la loi sur la r&#xE9;vision du concept salarial du 20 juin 1995, les anciennes parts d'exp&#xE9;rience des greffiers du Tribunal cantonal, des tribunaux de districts et du tribunal des mineurs, sont converties en nouvelles parts d'exp&#xE9;rience selon le bar&#xE8;me ci-apr&#xE8;s:<table><tableContent><row rowType="header"><cell>Anciennes parts d&amp;#39;exp&#xE9;rience</cell><cell>Pour cent</cell><cell>Nouvelles parts d&amp;#39;exp&#xE9;rience</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>1</cell><cell>3%</cell><cell>1.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>2</cell><cell>6%</cell><cell>3</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>3</cell><cell>9%</cell><cell>4.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>4</cell><cell>12%</cell><cell>6</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>5</cell><cell>15%</cell><cell>7.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>6</cell><cell>18%</cell><cell>9</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>7</cell><cell>21%</cell><cell>10.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>8</cell><cell>24%</cell><cell>12</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>9</cell><cell>27%</cell><cell>13.5</cell></row><row rowType="data"><cell>10</cell><cell>30%</cell><cell>15</cell></row></tableContent></table></mixedText>
                </partText>
              </partTexts>
            </articleText>
            <articleText>
              <partMetadata ID="Paragraph:28764">
                <partNumber>2</partNumber>
                <typeOfPart>A</typeOfPart>
              </partMetadata>
              <partTexts>
                <partText>
                  <mixedText lang="de">Die Gerichtsschreiber, deren Erfahrungsanteile gesamthaft 29 Prozent betragen, erhalten im folgenden Jahr einen Erfahrungsanteil von 1 Prozent.</mixedText>
                </partText>
                <partText>
                  <mixedText lang="fr">Les greffiers dont le total des parts d'exp&#xE9;rience s'&#xE9;l&#xE8;ve &#xE0; 29 pour cent re&#xE7;oivent l'ann&#xE9;e suivante une part d'exp&#xE9;rience de 1 pour cent.</mixedText>
                </partText>
              </partTexts>
            </articleText>
          </articleBody>
        </article>
        <article>
          <articleMetadata ID="Article:12493">
            <articleForm>Art.</articleForm>
